<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginna'n thil thiem leu hing,
 Zie khawvel apat hin;
 Pak ka nuom Hukdampa,
 Na hehpihna deihum.

[V2]
 Kipak lo thei kei puoi (2)
 Hukdampa Na nak liem;
 Tatna thisan pawtna,
 Etin nei tat dan hi, A na ka sa ta luoi.

[V3]
 2. Na lalna kumsawt gam,
 Pelin zie khawvelah;
 Ka gimnau Na paw zo,
 Sapsietna thing chungah.

[V4]
 3. Maa pi leh pute.
 Mansaksa van pielgal;
 Hehpihna thisan vang,
 Ken ka na mu kit tai.

[V5]
 4. Angel vamhaw lenna,
 Nitum lohna gam nuom;
 Aw Na thisan vangin,
 Bang tik leh ka tung dem?

[V6]
 5. Leiah liengvai mahleng,
 Lungsietin ei puiin;
 Ka thagau van gam ah,
 Nuom takin leng tana.

[V7]
 6. Na min lopi pakcha'n,
 Kipakin lasa'ng ka;
 Tuoilo pak Hukdampa,
 Na hawih chuom na zen e!</lyrics>
<title>Kipak Lothei Kei Puoi</title>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>89</hymn_number>
</song>